&lt;p data-start=&quot;274&quot; data-end=&quot;789&quot;&gt;Eon is the fastest growing enterprise SaaS company in history. We are the first cloud-native platform leveraging Cloud Data Posture Management (CDPM) to automate cloud backups, transform them into high-value, immediately usable assets, and dramatically reduce total cost of ownership for global enterprises.&lt;br data-start=&quot;584&quot; data-end=&quot;587&quot;&gt;As we continue to scale our GTM organization, we are building our first layer of regional leadership to drive revenue performance, develop exceptional teams, and accelerate our expansion across the U.S.&lt;/p&gt;
